message.body: Hi, yesterday went by in school work and apartment organizing. Still feeling lousy, how are things with you?
feeling depressed. i don't think the wellbutrin is doing mch beyond making me feel anxious.
Oh no, you do have a lot going on right now, depression is understandable. When do you see your therapist?
i'm going to the psychiatrist in a week. he is going to change my meds. pete told me i was being mean to him today. i kind of was but didn't realize it.
You shouldn't feel bad, you are under a lot of pressure and are essentially responsible for both of you. It's hard to control yourself when you are stressed like that. I'm sorry.
i guess. i was asking him if he was able to the call the psychiatrists and interview himself or if i needed to do it. i said it in a mean voice. i don't
like being in charge of that stuff - i guess it shows.
